title: Listen To This If You Feel Depressed
itunes:author: Joey Kidney
itunes:subtitle: How To Handle Depression
itunes:summary:
Feeling depressed? Let's talk about it. Often times we get these negative thoughts when we are in public scenarios with friends or out playing sports. Fighting off those negative thoughts in your head can be difficult, so this is the method I use.
